In China, winter sports are the next big thing, as the Beijing 2022 Winter Olympic Games are less than two months away. Getting 300 million people involved in winter sports was once China's vision for hosting Winter Olympics. That's one fifth of its own population and more than the combined populations of Russia, Germany and Canada, the three winter sports titans. How can China realize this ambitious vision? In this specialÂ episode of Unboxing Beijing 2022, CGTN's Liu Xiaoxian unboxes the winter sports gift box.